The paper also discusses the use of cryptographic primitives, such as homomorphic encryption, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The goal of the paper is to minimize the number of black-box calls and communication overhead, which involves optimization techniques commonly used in algorithms and complexity theory (cs.CC).
